OL,3,CTeenager stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath, court hears
OL,6,FWatch Richard Payne's report from
OL,7,Foutside Bristol Crown Court
OL,9,FA teenage boy googled "What happens if
OL,10,Fyou kill" minutes after stabbing a
OL,11,Fnine-year-old girl to death, a court
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FThe 16-year-old stabbed Aria Thorpe
OL,15,Fonce in the chest at a house in Weston-
OL,16,Fsuper-Mare, North Somerset, in
OL,17,FDecember last year.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@IO]
