CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781678874
OL,3,CTeenager stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath, court hears
OL,6,FAfter fleeing the property, he walked
OL,7,Fto a nearby railway station where he
OL,8,Ftold young people gathered there that
OL,9,Fhe had stabbed a child, Bristol Crown
OL,10,FCourt heard.
OL,12,F"You'll see it on the news later," he
OL,13,Ftold them.
OL,15,F"I was playing around with a knife.
OL,16,F(She) walked into the knife. I
OL,17,Faccidentally stabbed her with a really
OL,18,Fbig knife."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@bO]wD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
