PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781678874
OL,3,CTeenager stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath, court hears
OL,6,FHe told one of the group, who he knew:
OL,7,F"Yo (name) I'm a murderer. I
OL,8,Faccidentally killed someone."
OL,10,FWhile one of them distracted the
OL,11,Fteenager, another was able to ring
OL,12,Fpolice and alert them to what the
OL,13,Fdefendant was saying.
OL,15,FOne of the children later told police:
OL,16,F"He said he had done something really
OL,17,Fbad and did not know what to do.
OL,19,F"He asked if he could search something
OL,20,Fon Google. He then said, 'I'm done
OL,21,Ffor. Why have I done this'."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@]O]xD@AOU{D@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
