PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781678874
OL,3,CTeenager stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath, court hears
OL,6,FThe teenager, who cannot be identified
OL,7,Ffor legal reasons, was arrested
OL,8,Fminutes later sitting on the floor of
OL,9,Fa carriage of a train waiting to leave
OL,10,Fthe station.
OL,12,FThe teenager told detectives in a
OL,13,Fprepared statement: "I grabbed a knife
OL,14,Fand stabbed her in the chest. I didn't
OL,15,Fuse a lot of force, but it was a big
OL,16,Fknife. I don't know why I did it, it
OL,17,Fjust happened.
OL,26,@uD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
