PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781678874
OL,3,CTeenager stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath, court hears
OL,6,F"I walked over and stabbed her. She
OL,7,Ffell to the floor. I left and went to
OL,8,Fthe train station to get a train and
OL,9,Fto get away."
OL,11,FThe teenager denies charges of murder
OL,12,Fand manslaughter.
OL,14,FRay Tully KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,15,Fjury: "He admits that he had hold of
OL,16,Fthe knife in his hand at the time the
OL,17,Ffatal wound occurred.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@MO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
