PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781678874
OL,3,CTeenager stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath, court hears
OL,6,F"He says at the time they were
OL,7,F'playfighting' when he 'jabbed' the
OL,8,Fknife towards Aria, that was done in
OL,9,Forder to 'scare her'.
OL,11,F"He expected her to 'flinch'. Instead
OL,12,F'she moved towards him and was fatally
OL,13,Fwounded'.
OL,15,F"Soon after the fatal incident, he
OL,16,Ftold a group of young people that Aria
OL,17,Fhad either 'walked' or 'run' on to the
OL,18,Fblade of the knife as he was holding
OL,19,Fit."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@DO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
