PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781678874
OL,3,CTeenager stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath, court hears
OL,6,FThe court heard a friend of Aria's
OL,7,Ffamily discovered her body in the
OL,8,Fhouse and alerted the emergency
OL,9,Fservices.
OL,11,FA post-mortem examination found Aria
OL,12,Fhad suffered a single stab wound to
OL,13,Fthe chest.
OL,15,FThe trial before Mrs Justice O'Farrell
OL,16,Fcontinues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
